description:
TAG TEAM LEAGUE

TEAM RED
Ariel X & Samantha Sin
Combined HT: 127”
Combined WT: 235lbs
Record: (0-1)

TEAM BLUE
Isis Love & Jade Marxxx
Combined HT:133”
Combined WT: 265lbs
Record:(0-0)

Welcome to Ultimate Surrender’s second league match. This is how Red vs Blue should be. Four girls, non-scripted, real tag team action..

The rules are set: (1) Three tags per team, per round. (2) Three 12-minute non-scripted wrestling rounds. (3) Last round consists of the winners tying up, dominating, humiliating, and brutally fucking the losers.

Team Red: Lost their first match and cannot afford to lose another. Anchored by veteran Ariel “The Assassin” X. This team lost its first match by only 17pts in the very last minute of the match. Since Samantha “The Python” Sin is getting stronger with each match, the Team hopes to dominate and fuck the more experienced Blue team.

Team Blue: The only team to feature wrestlers from the very first season of Ultimate Surrender, their experience is unmatched by any other team in the league. Anchored by beautiful Isis “The Goddess” Love, this team is favored to take home the Championships. With Jade “The Trouper” Marxxx at The Goddess’s side, this team is fast, big, and strong.

Once again the match went down to the last minute, and we have a loser after 36 minutes of brutal wrestling. Heart breaking for the losers, but sweet, sweet victory for the winners! Which team got fucked and humiliated for losing? Which team got tied up and dominated by the victors?
title: TAG TEAM LEAGUE Team Red vs Team Blue
